post.description:
Move assets into given mass import.

The owner of a waiting asset that have never been available (if available asset's workflow has been reset it
becomes waiting again) will be changed to the owner of the target mass import

<p>request example:</p>

<pre>
      /rest/mp/v1.0/assets/import/mass-imports/638/assets
 </pre>

<p>request parameter example:</p>

<pre>
          [77, 78, 89, 141, 142, 143, 190]
 </pre>

<p>response example:</p>

<pre>
{
     "errors": [
         {
             "@type": "insufficient_privileges",
             "messages": [
                 {
                     "defaultMessage": "User has insufficient rights to mass import with ID 87",
                     "messageCode": "MP_E02027",
                     "params": {
                         "id": 87
                     }
                 },
                 {
                     "defaultMessage": "User has insufficient rights to mass import with ID 538",
                     "messageCode": "MP_E02027",
                     "params": {
                         "id": 538
                     }
                 }
             ],
             "status": 403
         }
     ]
 }
 </pre>

__Security Roles Allowed:__ PIMEDIA_DATABASE_MODULE_ACCESS

For the given mass-import's assets (only red ones and with just one version) searches for existing matching assets
(green, accessible etc.) to which can become new versions. Source and target assets will be matched 1:1, i.e.
neither more than one matching target assets for one source asset, neither vice versa.

<p>request example:</p>

<pre>
      /rest/mp/v1.0/assets/import/mass-imports/1291/matches
 </pre>

<p>request parameter example:</p>

<pre>
 {
   "matchType": "ASSET_ID",
   "separatorType": "PREFIX",
   "separator": ".",
   "vdbUuids": ["6f7a382b-3901-490b-9b4d-8fe5638b47ab", "9e849dfc-dfd5-4468-8023-93f0c062cb6f", "9834a801-0997-4dae-a75e-979238886bec"]
 }

 </pre>

<p>response example:</p>
<pre>
 {
     "log": {
         "warnings": [
             {
                 "@type": "warning",
                 "messages": [
                     {
                         "defaultMessage": "The asset M-890 may contain linked images. When uploading a new version, the links to images inside the new version are lost. To keep the links, upload the document and its linked images as a ZIP file via the import function and extract the ZIP afterwards in the import folder.",
                         "messageCode": "MP_W02007",
                         "params": {
                             "assetId": "M-890"
                         }
                     }
                 ]
             }
         ]
     },
     "matches": [
         {
             "sourceAssetId": 896,
             "targetAssetId": 890
         }
     ]
 }
 </pre>

__Security Roles Allowed:__ PIMEDIA_DATABASE_MODULE_ACCESS

