get.description:
list history of official versions of an asset.
Optional parameter hideDeleted will hide already deleted versions of the asset from the returned history.


<p> request example: </p>

<pre>
        /rest/mp/v1.0/assets/151446/official-history?hideDeleted=true
 </pre>

<p> response example: </p>

<pre>
     {
         "officialHistory": [
             {
             "assetVersionNumber": 2,
             "officialFrom": "2018-07-25T11:01:09",
             "officialTo": "2018-07-25T11:10:35"
             },
